tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
Facing a sudden dental emergency with a broken crown before an important workshop, I sought immediate help via Practo and visited Dr. Shibani. She quickly understood my anxiety, coordinated with my dentist, and fixed both crowns within just two days over the weekend. Dr. Shibani not only addressed the issue efficiently but also provided valuable insights on oral care. Her professionalism, combined with reasonable pricing, makes her one of the best dentists I've encountered. Thanks to her, I attended my workshop confidently. Highly recommend Dr. Shibani for top-notch dental care.

Thank you, Dr. Shibani.
